headline.print_headline: Schippers Wins Second Gold With Year's Best Time
headline.main: Schippers Wins Second Gold With Year's Best Time

lead_paragraph: Dutch sprinter Dafne Schippers ran the fastest 200 meters this year on Friday to collect her second gold medal of the European championships.
